<center><font size=7><b>Moon Alert</b></font></center>
<center>Number of entries found: 5</center><p>
<center>
<table width=600>
<TR><TD bgcolor="blue" background=""><font color="white"><b><i>Multiface pokes</i></b></font></td></tr>
<TR><TD>Ocean's
<I>Moon Alert</I>- POKE 39754
for endless lives, POKE
42404,x for 'x' lives (up to 14
only) and POKE 42654,195
for immortality!
 <i>(Le Page Said, Nicholas Smith in Your Spectrum issue 11)</i> 

<br><hr>
POKE 42249,24 to stop
the time going down, and
POKEs 42585,2 and 52596,2
to keep it scrolling fast in all
parts of the screen
 <i>(Le Page Said, Nicholas Smith in Your Spectrum issue 11)</i> 

<br><hr>
	On the international front,
<B>Bjarne Nielsen</B> of Denmark
sent in a 100-lives POKE for
<I>Moon Alert</I> - POKE
42404,255
 <i>(Bjarne Nielsen in Your Spectrum issue 12)</i> 

<br><hr>
<table border="0">
<tr>
<td WIDTH="200" ALIGN="LEFT"><B><U>DESCRIPTION</B></U></TD>
<td WIDTH="200" ALIGN="LEFT"><B><U>POKE(s)</B></U></TD>
</TR>
<tr><td>Infinite Lives</td><td>39754,0</td></tr>
<tr><td>Infinite Energy</td><td>42654,195</td></tr>
<tr><td>Infinite Time</td><td>42249,24</td></tr>
<tr><td>Immediate scroll</td><td>42585,2:42596,2</td></tr>
<tr><td>Lives = x</td><td>42404,x (x= 1-255)</td></tr>
</table>
<BR><BR><B>The only problem with the Infinite Time POKE is that it takes AGES when you get
your bonus (just after the dodgy copyright-infringing Indiana Jones tune :) )
<br>

&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <i>(Gerard Sweeney in Hack Attack III)</i> 

<br><hr>
On Moon Alert, POKE 42404,255 will give 100 lives.
 <i>(Derek Ribeirio in Sinclair User issue 39)</i> 
<br>
</td></tr>
</table></center><P>
